data.description: Don't miss this 4 bed 3 bath walkout ranch with no backyard neighbors located in Gretna schools situated in Whitetail Creek! Bright & open main level with LVP flooring boasting a sizable living room with a beautiful cozy gas fire place and a kitchen sure to fit your needs featuring stainless steel appliances, plenty of counter and cabinet space, center island with additional seating, and a great dining area with sliding door access to the deck. Primary suite with 3/4 en suite bath offering dual sinks, shower, and nice-sized walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms, a full bath, and laundry room complete the main level. Downstairs, you'll find an expansive family room, 4th bedroom, and 3/4 bath great for guests. Check out the bonus partially finished den in the basement - the perfect hideaway for movie nights! Awesome outdoor space with deck, private covered deck below & extended patio overlooking a fully fenced yard, green space & mature tree line. Walking distance to elementary school!
